The very unconventional breast pump used in my last produced play. Sadly, I didn't get a picture when the "nipples" were lit up.

2012 was the first year since 2003 that I did not have a play produced. This is not a random bit of bad luck. 2012 was also the first year since 2003 that I did not send out any plays to theatres or festivals. I also wasn’t writing anything new.
